            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 8: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Applicant will receive an Application ID/Reference Number. Save or print the acknowledgement for future tracking."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": ""
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "process_md": "**Step 1:** Visit the [official website](https://daadconline.gujarat.gov.in/) of the Dr. Ambedkar Antyodaya Vikas Nigam (SC).\n**Step 2:** On the top menu bar, click on &quot;Apply Now&quot;.\n**Step 3:** Click on the loan scheme name. \n**Step 4:** Select the loan category and fill in the loan amount.\n**Step 5:** Fill out the Application Form, enter the following details:\n\n- Personal Information: Name, gender, date of birth, caste, etc.\n- Address Information: Permanent and correspondence address\n- Income Details: Monthly family income and source\n- Loan Requirement: Amount needed, proposed use (e.g., business, self-employment)\n- Bank Account Details: For loan disbursement\n\n**Step 6:** Upload scanned copies of the Caste certificate, Income certificate, Aadhaar card, Passport-size photo, Bank passbook (first page), and Residence proof.\n**Step 7:** Double-check all details. Click on “Preview” to verify. If all details are correct, click “Submit”.\n**Step 8:** Applicant will receive an Application ID/Reference Number. Save or print the acknowledgement for future tracking.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
